'''甘露庚酮糖'''（{{lang-en|Mannoheptulose}}）是一种[[庚糖|庚糖]]，即有七个碳原子的[[单糖|单糖]]。它是[[己糖激酶|己糖激酶]]的[[酶抑制剂|抑制剂]]，通过竞争性地与己糖激酶结合来阻断[[葡萄糖|葡萄糖]]的[[磷酸化|磷酸化]]。结果是葡萄糖的降解被抑制。<small>D</small>-甘露庚酮糖最早在[[鳄梨|鳄梨]]中发现<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Overexpression of Arabidopsis Hexokinase in Tomato Plants Inhibits Growth, Reduces Photosynthesis, and Induces Rapid Senescence|url=https://academic.oup.com/plcell/article/11/7/1253-1266/6008439|last=Dai|first=Nir|last2=Schaffer|first2=Arthur|date=1999-07|journal=The Plant Cell|issue=7|doi=10.1105/tpc.11.7.1253|volume=11|pages=1253–1266|language=en|issn=1040-4651|pmc=PMC144264|pmid=10402427|last3=Petreikov|first3=Marina|last4=Shahak|first4=Yosepha|last5=Giller|first5=Yuri|last6=Ratner|first6=Kira|last7=Levine|first7=Alex|last8=Granot|first8=David|access-date=2021-11-10|archive-date=2022-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220111172118/https://academic.oup.com/plcell/article/11/7/1253-1266/6008439|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

有研究指出，甘露庚酮糖會抑制[[胰島素|胰島素]]分泌<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Effect of 2-Deoxy-D-Glucose and Mannoheptulose on the Insulin Response to Amino Acids in Rabbits|url=http://diabetes.diabetesjournals.org/cgi/doi/10.2337/diab.21.1.1|last=Lucke|first=C.|last2=Kagan|first2=A.|date=1972-01-01|journal=Diabetes|issue=1|doi=10.2337/diab.21.1.1|volume=21|pages=1–5|language=en|issn=0012-1797|last3=Adelman|first3=N.|last4=Glick|first4=S. M.}}</ref>。 This inhibition occurs because when mannoheptulose is present the glycolysis is inhibited (because there is no production of glucose-6-P) therefore no increase in ATP concentration which is required to close the KATP channel in the beta cells of the pancreas causing a diminution of calcium entry and insulin secretion.
